<h1 style="color:#0099FF">Obstetrics/Gynecology</h1>

<p>DRMHOPE <b>Obstetrics and Gynecology </b>solution is a web based application that addresses the administrative and clinical 
needs of a gynecology and obstetrics practice. It can be configured for stand-alone practices as well as the Obstetrics
 and Gynecology specilities within a hospital. With built-in system templates specifically for the<b> Obstetrics and 
 Gynecology physician,</b> they can be easily customized to create new templates to match your own best practices.</p>

<h2>Benefits</h2>
<ul>
<li>	This obstetrics and gynecology software helps in saving time by allowing access to the complete obstetrics and 
gynecology patient records in one place</li>
<li>	Manage patient schedules and appointments</li>
<li>	Allow all clinicians in a practice to view a common patient electronic medical record</li>
<li>	Integrate with medical imaging software, allowing access to patient's medical images</li>
<li>	Reduce effort duplication</li>
<li>	Improve patient's care</li>
<li>	Obstetrics and gynecology information contains all the details of the patients.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Features</h2>
<ul>
<li>	Ostetrics and Gynecology specific templates for annual well-woman exams, new prenatal encounters, post-natal follow up</li>
<li>Ostetrics and Gynecology reporting with voice recognition</li>
<li>	Patient medical records and history</li>
<li>	Patient treatment plan and flow sheets</li>
<li>	Gestation calculator for quick delivery date estimates</li>
<li>	Risk factors</li>
<li>	Flow sheets - track trends of patients' lab data over a period of time.</li>
<li>	Patient scheduling and appointments</li>
<li>Patient medical image viewing</li>
<li>	Lab integration</li>
<li>	Medication records</li>
<li>	Alerts and Reminders</li>
<li>	Reports and Dashboards </li>
</ul>
